---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="About our service - MiraHikari's Vmail"
  description={Astro.locals.runtime.env.SITE_DESCRIPTION}

>
  <div class="mx-10 mt-24 text-primary">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px]">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold" id="about">
        About{' '}
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8">
        <strong>MiraHikari's VMAIL</strong> is a Virtual temporary email service.{
          ' '
        }
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        You can get a temporary email without revealing any personal
        information, which greatly protects your privacy.{' '}
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        It supports selecting one domain names, making it convenient for you to
        use in different scenarios.{' '}
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        100% running on the <strong>Cloudflare </strong> network, providing you with
        a super-fast experience.{' '}

        We use Cloudflare D1 to store email data, which ensures the security and
        reliability of your emails. You can check the <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a
        > for more details
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4">
        Misuse of the temporary email service not only violates our terms of
        service but can also impact the normal use of other users. We encourage
        each user to use our services responsibly to ensure that resources are
        allocated and used appropriately.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
